 ABUJA: The ruling All Progressives Congress APC has warned the opposition against politicizing the first incidence of Coronavirus in the country, saying the President Muhammadu Buhari led administration should be commended for acting swiftly to contain the disease. March 1, 2020 In "News" The All Progressives Congress, APC, and Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, were yesterday locked in a war of words over the index case of coronavirus recorded in Lagos last weekend. March 2, 2020 In "News" Twenty Four governors of the ruling All Progressives Congress APC have blamed the current wave of separatist agitation on weak governance as provided across the different tiers of government. June 22, 2017 In "News"